  "id": "html-1771879771970",
  "title": "Índice de flexibilidad curricular",
  "type": "html",
  "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"es\">\n\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>Justificación - Oferta Internacional - Unitrópico</title>\n  <!-- Fuente Montserrat y CSS base -->\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../css_presentaciones/unitropico_base.css\">\n  <style>\n    /* =========================\n       ESTILOS ADICIONALES\n    ========================= */\n    html,\n    body {\n      height: 100%;\n      margin: 0;\n      overflow-x: hidden;\n      background: url(\"../img/background-1.jpg\") no-repeat center center fixed;\n      background-size: cover;\n      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;\n    }\n\n    /* Navbar */\n    .navbar-img {\n      width: 100%;\n      background: var(--verde-1);\n      text-align: center;\n    }\n\n    .navbar-img img {\n      width: 100%;\n      height: auto;\n      max-height: 110px;\n      object-fit: contain;\n      display: block;\n    }\n\n    /* Contenedor principal */\n    .container {\n      max-width: 1100px;\n      margin: 30px auto;\n      padding: 0 25px;\n    }\n\n    /* Estilos de la tabla de Flexibilidad */\n    .flex-table-container {\n      width: 100%;\n      overflow-x: auto;\n      margin-top: 10px;\n      margin-bottom: 50px;\n    }\n\n    .flex-table {\n      width: 100%;\n      border-collapse: collapse;\n      text-align: center;\n      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;\n    }\n\n    .flex-table th,\n    .flex-table td {\n      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);\n      padding: 18px 10px;\n      vertical-align: middle;\n    }\n\n    .flex-table th {\n      font-weight: 700;\n      font-size: 1.05rem;\n    }\n\n    .flex-table td {\n      font-size: 1.1rem;\n    }\n\n    .bg-dark-green {\n      background-color: #215a4f;\n      /* Verde oscuro ligeramente desaturado */\n    }\n\n    .bg-gold {\n      background-color: #c9af70;\n      /* Color caqui / arena de la imagen */\n    }\n\n    .text-white {\n      color: #ffffff;\n    }\n\n    /* Responsive */\n    @media (max-width: 768px) {\n      .container {\n        margin: 15px;\n        padding: 0 15px;\n      }\n\n      .section-header-line h2 {\n        font-size: 1.5rem !important;\n      }\n\n      .line-gold {\n        width: 100% !important;\n        max-width: 550px;\n      }\n\n      .line-gray {\n        width: 80% !important;\n        max-width: 450px;\n      }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n\n<body>\n  <!-- Navbar de imagen -->\n  <div class=\"navbar-img\">\n    <img src=\"media/denominacion/navbar.png\" alt=\"Navbar Unitropico\">\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"container\">\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n    <!-- Título del artículo (alineado izquierda) -->\n    <div class=\"top-left-title subtitulo text-verde-1\">\n      <span class=\"text-bronce-1\">Artículo 2.5.3.2.3.2.4.</span> Aspectos curriculares - a) Componentes formativos\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Encabezado centrado de Flexibilidad -->\n    <div class=\"section-header-line\" style=\"margin-bottom: 40px; text-align: center; padding-top: 10px;\">\n      <h2 style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 2rem; line-height: 1.35; color: #007580; margin: 0 0 10px 0;\">\n        Índice de flexibilidad curricular del<br>\n        <strong style=\"color: #004b40; font-weight: 700;\">programa Ingeniería en Inteligencia<br>Artificial</strong>\n      </h2>\n      <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0px;\">\n        <div class=\"line-gold\" style=\"width: 550px; height: 3px; background-color: #ba9b5e; border-radius: 2px;\"></div>\n        <div class=\"line-gray\" style=\"width: 450px; height: 6px; background-color: #e0e0e0; border-radius: 3px;\"></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Contenido: Tabla de Flexibilidad -->\n    <div class=\"flex-table-container\">\n      <table class=\"flex-table\">\n        <thead>\n          <tr class=\"bg-dark-green text-white\">\n            <th style=\"width: 22%;\">Programa</th>\n            <th style=\"width: 18%;\">Créditos<br>obligatorios<br>(A)</th>\n            <th style=\"width: 22%;\">Créditos optativos y<br>electivos<br>(B)</th>\n            <th style=\"width: 18%;\">Total de<br>créditos<br>C=A+B</th>\n            <th style=\"width: 20%;\">Índice de<br>flexibilidad%<br>D=(B/C)* 100</th>\n          </tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody>\n          <tr class=\"bg-gold text-white\" style=\"font-weight: 700;\">\n            <td style=\"font-size: 1.15rem;\">Ingeniería en<br>Inteligencia<br>Artificial</td>\n            <td>123</td>\n            <td>25</td>\n            <td>148</td>\n            <td>16,89%</td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</body>\n\n</html>",
  "allowScripts": true,
  "hotspots": []
}